                                    ISO 21001:2018 specifies requirements for a management system for educational
                                    organizations (EOMS) when such an organization:
                                    <br>
                                    <br>
                                    a) needs to demonstrate its ability to support the acquisition and development of
                                    competence through teaching, learning or research;
                                    <br>
                                    <br>
                                    b) aims to enhance the satisfaction of learners, other beneficiaries and staff
                                    through the effective application of its EOMS, including processes for improvement
                                    of the system and assurance of conformity to the requirements of learners and other
                                    beneficiaries.
                                    <br>
